OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSunny spells
OL,6,Fand blustery showers persisting into
OL,7,Fthe evening. Showers gradually fading
OL,8,Fwith clearer spells developing
OL,9,Fovernight but remaining windy with
OL,10,Fsome strong gusts possible.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FDry to start the day with
OL,13,Fpatchy cloud around but still a little
OL,14,Fbreezy. Showers developing during the
OL,15,Fafternoon but less heavy than on
OL,16,FThursday with the wind easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
