OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMostly
OL,6,Fwet and grey on Saturday, turning
OL,7,Fdrier for most on Sunday with isolated
OL,8,Fshowers. A wet start to Monday but
OL,9,Fslowly improving as the day
OL,10,Fprogresses. Temperatures around normal.
